Package org.infinispan.server.memcached.logging

Interface Log

All Superinterfaces:
org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
@MessageLogger(projectCode="ISPN") public interface Log extends org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
Log abstraction for the Memcached server module. For this module, message ids ranging from 11001 to 12000 inclusively have been reserved.
